31#include "gmp.h"
32#include "gmp-impl.h"
33
34void
35mpq_set_z (mpq_ptr dest, mpz_srcptr src)
36{
37 mp_size_t num_size;
38 mp_size_t abs_num_size;
39 mp_ptr dp;
40
41 num_size = SIZ (src);
42 abs_num_size = ABS (num_size);
43 dp = MPZ_NEWALLOC (NUM(dest), abs_num_size);
44 SIZ(NUM(dest)) = num_size;
45 MPN_COPY (dp, PTR(src), abs_num_size);
46
47 PTR(DEN(dest))[0] = 1;
48 SIZ(DEN(dest)) = 1;
49}
